DOC.brief_title: Objective Structured Assessment Technical Skills ( OSATS ) Evaluation Shoulder Dystocia Management
DOC.detailed_description: We prospectively randomize probands 30 min hands-on ( group 1 ) 30 min demonstration ( group 2 ) training session teach standardized SD algorithm scheme pelvic training model . Probands test 22 item Objective Structured Assessment Technical Skills ( OSATS ) score system train 72 hour thereafter . OSATS score primary outcome . Performance time ( PT ) , self assessment ( SA ) , confidence ( CON ) , global rating scale ( GRS ) secondary outcome . Statistics beperformed use Mann-Whitney U-test , chi-square test , multivariable logistic regression analysis .
DOC.keyword: To assess effectiveness hands-on training versus expert demonstration
